*1975–76 Out of playoffs.
*1976–77 Lost to S.S. Marie Greyhounds 3 games to 1 in first round.
*1977–78 Defeated Oshawa Generals 9 points to 3 in quarter-finals. Defeated Ottawa 67&#x27;s 9 points to 7 in semi-finals. Defeated Hamilton Fincups 8 points to 6 in finals. OHL CHAMPIONS Finished Memorial Cup round-robin in first place, earned berth in finals. Lost to New Westminster Bruins 7–4 in the championship game.
