* Volume A: 1999
* Volume B: 1997 
* Volume C: 1997 
* Volume D: 1998 
* Volume E: 1998

==Fourth edition==
The fourth edition was published in the following years:
* Volume A: 2001
* Volume B: 2002 
* Volume C: 2000
* Volume D: 2004 
* Volume E: 2008

==Fifth edition==
The fifth edition was published in the following years:
* Volume C: 2006
* Volume B part 1 [ECO codes: B00–B49]: 2020
* Volume B part 2 [ECO codes: B50-B99]: 2021

